Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
Call TEXTE(15597,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
## Action STD
Call AS_DOSDES(VALEUR) From PYRCOP
If mkstat=2
 [M]DOSDES(INDIC) = VALEUR
 Affzo DOSDES(INDIC) : mkstat = 2
Endif
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_DOSDES(zc) From W1PYRCOP
Gosub _AFF
End

